OL,3,C'Gratuitous' and 'intense' violence
OL,4,Cused to kill grandfather, court hears
OL,6,FA teenager accused of murdering an 80-
OL,7,Fyear-old man in a park by punching and
OL,8,Fkicking him used "gratuitous" and
OL,9,F"intense" violence before leaving his
OL,10,Fvictim for dead, the prosecution at
OL,11,Fhis trial has said.
OL,13,FThe 15-year-old boy denies murder and
OL,14,Fan alternative count of manslaughter
OL,15,Fin relation to the death of Bhim
OL,16,FKohli, who died in hospital a day
OL,17,Fafter suffering fractured ribs and a
OL,18,Fbroken neck.
