OL,3,C'Gratuitous' and 'intense' violence
OL,4,Cused to kill grandfather, court hears
OL,6,FThe boy's co-defendant, a 13-year-old
OL,7,Fgirl, denies manslaughter after
OL,8,Fallegedly encouraging him to attack Mr
OL,9,FKohli in Franklin Park in Braunstone
OL,10,FTown, near Leicester, on September 1
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FThe teenagers cannot be named for
OL,14,Flegal reasons because of their age.
OL,16,FAt Leicester Crown Court on Tuesday,
OL,17,Fprosecutor Harpreet Sandhu KC used his
OL,18,Fclosing speech to accuse the youth of
OL,19,Fhaving a desire to cause really
OL,20,Fserious physical harm to Mr Kohli.
