OL,3,C'Gratuitous' and 'intense' violence
OL,4,Cused to kill grandfather, court hears
OL,6,FMr Sandhu told the jury that two video
OL,7,Fclips filmed by the girl showed the
OL,8,Fboy accused of murder without either
OL,9,Fof his sliders on his feet, and
OL,10,Ffootage showed him using a slider to
OL,11,Fslap Mr Kohli.
OL,13,FHe also alleged that the 13 year old
OL,14,Fgirl had prior knowledge that a
OL,15,Fviolent attack was coming.
OL,17,FMr Sandhu told the jury: "It began to
OL,18,Fbe filmed before (the boy) used a
OL,19,Fslider to slap Bhim Kohli to the face.
