OL,6,FThe youth had no reason at all to hit
OL,7,FMr Kohli, Mr Sandhu said, adding that
OL,8,Fthe boy's actions had been "gratuitous
OL,9,Fviolence against a man who was
OL,10,Fdefenceless and a man who, because he
OL,11,Fwas on the ground, was in a vulnerable
OL,12,Fposition."
OL,14,FHe continued: "He was prepared to use
OL,15,Fviolence when it wasn't needed. His
OL,16,Finstinct when he first approached Bhim
OL,17,FKohli was to use violence.
